      company_info:
        "<h2>Essentials</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><mark>Inclusive of Airport access fee, operates at both Terminals</mark></li>\r\n  <li>Return at any time and we will deliver your car 24/7 365 Days</li>\r\n  <li>Gatwick Airport Approved Meet &amp; Greet operator</li>\r\n  <li>Approved Meet &amp; Greet Operator, top quality Recommended Service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n<p>We provide meet and greet services helping you save money and enjoy your time away knowing your car is safe. We are different to most meet and greet services, and hope you will agree that we provide a new standard for service levels and good old hard work.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Book This Parking Space?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Perfect for disabled passengers, eliminating the need to catch a transfer bus</li>\r\n  <li>Assistance available for getting in and out of your vehicle</li>\r\n  <li>Specially adapted vehicles accommodated with prior arrangement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Disabled Info</h2>\r\n<p>This parking is perfect for disabled passengers as you won&apos;t need to catch a transfer bus. If you need help getting in and out of your vehicle or if you have a specially adapted vehicle, please call us and one of our team will contact the Service Provider for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Insurance</h2>\r\n<p>All drivers are fully insured to drive your vehicle. Please check Service Provider&apos;s terms for further insurance details or ask us if you have any queries.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Vehicles</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Vehicle must be in roadworthy condition/legal</li>\r\n  <li>Chauffeur may refuse to drive unsafe or non-road legal vehicles</li>\r\n  <li>Extra charges for vehicles not fitting into a standard parking space, arrange with Service Provider prior to booking</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Amendments/Cancellations</h2>\r\n<p>Allowed up to 48 hours prior to drop-off date. Admin charges applicable on cancellations. Check our terms for full details. If your return is delayed and you park for longer than you have booked, extra days parking will be charged. Please check Service Provider&apos;s terms for rates.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Hints, Tips, and Additional Info</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Take a copy of your confirmation email with you on your day of travel</li>\r\n  <li>Check junk/spam mail folders for important emails</li>\r\n  <li>Allow sufficient time for drop-off and airport departure procedures</li>\r\n  <li>Contact Service Provider for any delays or changes in drop-off/return times</li>\r\n  <li>Parking is at your own risk; avoid keeping valuables in your car</li>\r\n  <li>Inspect vehicle carefully at pickup and report any issues to driver</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Important</h2>\r\n<p>Service is operated by Sure Parking Limited. Full instructions will be provided in the booking confirmation email. Compare Parking provides price comparison and acts as booking agents for available Service Providers.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
